> Module ModuleA

# Synthetic Multi-Module Fixture — Module A

This module declares `field_a` only. The shared `naming-manifest.yaml`
also declares `field_b`, which lives in Module B. The per-file
divergence check on this module alone would falsely flag `field_b` as
missing; the aggregated check across the work-list does not.

```catala-metadata
declaration scope ScopeA:
  output field_a content integer
```

```catala
scope ScopeA:
  definition field_a equals 1
```
